{"title":"1×11 Campagnolo Record and half a handlebar: Simon Warren’s Time NX","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/simon-warren-bike-national-hill-climb-2023","date":1699019463000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/simon-warren-bike-national-hill-climb-2023\">1×11 Campagnolo Record and half a handlebar: Simon Warren’s Time NX</a></p>\n\n<p>Author of ‘100 Greatest Cycling Climbs’, Simon Warren knows all about ascents and his Time NX is a case in point. In true hill climb style, the drop bars have been sawn down and the stem has been slammed and trimmed to size. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike is running Schwalbe Podium tubular 22mm tyres and rim brake Zipp 303 carbon wheels, and even the valves have been trimmed down to sit flush with the rims. In a bid to save even more weight, the carbon Selle Italia SLR saddle has been drilled with holes and electrical tape has been used in lieu of handlebar wrap. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep scrolling for up-close pictures of this lightweight build. </p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-bike-helmet\">Best bike helmet: Buyer’s guide to road and gravel bike helmets from under £100</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-road-bike\">Best road bikes: Best bikes from under £1,000 to over £10,000</a>\r\n                    