ites/9/2023/11/simon_warren_time_hill_climb_national_2023-2-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Charlotte Head</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Simon Warren’s Time NX spec</h2>\n\n\n\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Frameset</td><td>Time NX</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Weight</td><td>5.9kg</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Groupset</td><td>Campagnolo Record 11-speed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Stem</td><td>Easton</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Wheels</td><td>Zipp 303 rim brake</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Tyres</td><td>Continental Podium TT tubular 22mm</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Saddle</td><td>Selle Italia SLR carbon</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/simon-warren-bike-national-hill-climb-2023\">1×11 Campagnolo Record and half a handlebar: Simon Warren’s Time NX</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Charlotte Head &#124; Tech Writer","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"59ee5ffe933871a86c53dbbedd9b8a0a730f8008e430aeea32c3f9094b1791d8","category":"Cycling"}